snippet.title: Among Us - The Fungle - Map 5 Reveal Trailer 🍄🗺️  omggggggggggg
snippet.description:
We're super excited to announce our brand new map - The Fungle is coming to Among Us this October! The Crewmates might be in trouble crash landing on a deserted island filled with mushrooms, marshmallows, and... weird plants?

Read here: https://www.innersloth.com/new-map-the-fungle-coming-this-october/

Animations: Jake Clark
Trailer Editing: Derek Lieu

Among Us is a game of teamwork and betrayal for 4-15 players...in space! Play online or via local WiFi as you attempt to prepare your spaceship for departure, but beware as one or more random players among the Crew are Impostors bent on killing everyone. Try different roles, Hide n Seek mode, and customize your Crewmate!

------------------------------------------
